summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2737, for the improvement of 30th Avenue South from Irving Street to Holgate Street, all in the City of Seattle, by constructing watermains of proper dimensions and materials, under Ordinance No. 32469 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
